Meridiana 89 6th Floor, 08026, Barcelona (Spain), attaching a photocopy of your ID or equivalent valid identification document. You can also exercise your rights by a communication addressed to: privacy@wallapop.com. Finally, we remind you that you can file a claim with the Spanish Data Protection Agency, if you consider that Wallapop has violated your rights in terms of data protection.”
